</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5308339" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5308339" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5308339/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="67" startId="5.[136,229,826,848]" targetBox="[151,1436,190,802]" targetPageId="5">
